      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and clearly shows the marks of its years on the road. While it remains a reliable daily driver that will get you from point A to point B, potential buyers should note that the engine lacks the responsiveness of a newer model and the transmission shifts are less smooth than they once were. The exterior paint has some noticeable fading and minor dings, and the interior upholstery shows typical wear and tear from regular use. It is a solid, budget-friendly option for someone looking for utility over aesthetics.",
